Name: Average time from Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time between Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment across all successful payment variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time it takes Request Payment to be performed after Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time for Request Payment grouped by case:Amount
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of case:Amount

Name: Time elapsed from Request Payment to Payment Handled in variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average cycle time of Request Payment in variants where no rejections occurred
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE does not occur

Name: Minimum waiting time to Request Payment after the last approval step (e.g., Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR, Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER, or Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Request Payment in direct approval paths (without any rejection)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Time between Request Payment and Payment Handled compared to the time between Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for Request Payment in variants involving budget owner approval versus those without
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER occurs

Name: Total time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Request Payment in paths that skip budget owner and pre-approver steps
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment in domestic trip reimbursement cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Cycle time of Request Payment in variants that originate from resubmissions after rejection by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION occurs

Name: Total resolution time of Request Payment in cases processed entirely in 2018 versus 2017
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time it takes Request Payment to be executed after the final approval, segmented by department (inferred from case patterns in 2017 vs. university-wide in 2018)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'
